<font size="3" color="#FF7D00"><b>Solusek Ro meets his maker</b></font>
</td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="5" width="100%"><tr><td>
<font color="#FFFFFF"><b><a href="search.php?query=&amp;topic=13"><img src="images/topics/pix.gif" border="0" Alt="News" align="right" hspace="10" vspace="10"></a></B></font><br>
<font size="2" color="#FFFFFF"><center><b><h1>Solusek Ro DEAD!</h1><br><br><h2>Cha Ching!</h2></b><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/solusekcorpse.JPG><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/mask.JPG></center><br><br><br></center>Kapow, smack, poof, bang! One of our late night raids of 30 people and some twoboxed pack mules managed to put down Solusek Ro tonight. This has got to be one of the most kickass evenings in quite some time. We gently got the staff up the rectum on our first try. That AE is erotic. On 2nd try, everything was going good, he was at 50%, we had zero deaths, then we got repops. Yummy. Third try was smooth sailing. He went down without any problem whatsoever, zero casualties. I think he hurt someone's feelings, but apart from that it was all good. Khaunshar and Jmich got masks.<br><br><br><center><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/fire.JPG><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/pofire.JPG></center><br><br><br><br>We've also been playing around the other elemental zones and having a hell of a time too. Not much to say about it really, so I'll let the corpses speak for themselves...<br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/jivacorpse.JPG><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/protectorcorpse.JPG><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/cursedcorpse.JPG><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/griocorpse.JPG><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/calebcorpse.JPG><br><br><br>... and the loot ...<br><br><br><center><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/belt.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/greatsword.JPG><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/sword.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/ring.JPG><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/basalt.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/bbb.JPG><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/hammer.JPG><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/shard.JPG><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/sphere.JPG></center><br><br><br><br><br>Batman owns you.<br><br><br><b>Quotes of the Day</b><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/hratli.GIF><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/flippett.GIF><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/malaari.GIF><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/leandred.GIF><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/mokia.GIF><br><br><img src=http://www.amm-electronics.net/remedy/solusek/rinderwahn.GIF><br><br><br><b>~Arbaal</b></font>
